message: Be aware of what your children are doing online. Most of the kids that are being groomed into human trafficking are being groomed online first. They really shouldn't have a social media friend that they haven't met in person.

data.description: January is Human Trafficking Awareness Month, millions of people around the world become victims of human trafficking. With today's modern technology, people are often advertised online.
data.title: Keeping kids safe from human trafficking
